trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerType" /> class represents the type on which the XML Web service is based.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerType" /> 類別表示 XML Web Service 所依據的型別。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Type" /> on which this XML Web service is based.
trans-unit.target: 這個 XML Web Service 所依據的 <see cref="T:System.Type" />。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WebServiceProtocols" /> value that specifies the transmission protocols that are used to decrypt data sent in the XML Web service request.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WebServiceProtocols" /> 值，指定用於解密在 XML Web Service 要求中傳送之資料的傳輸通訊協定。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerType" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerType" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The key associated with the desired duplicate <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" />.
trans-unit.target: 與需要之重複 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" /> 相關聯的索引鍵。

trans-unit.source: Returns the duplicate <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" /> associated with the specified key.
trans-unit.target: 傳回與指定之索引鍵相關聯的重複 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" />。

trans-unit.source: The duplicate <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" /> associated with the specified key.
trans-unit.target: 與指定之索引鍵相關聯的重複 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" />。

trans-unit.source: The key associated with the desired <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" />.
trans-unit.target: 與需要之 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" /> 相關聯的索引鍵。

trans-unit.source: Returns the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" /> associated with the specified key.
trans-unit.target: 傳回與指定之索引鍵相關聯的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" />。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" /> associated with the specified key.
trans-unit.target: 與指定之索引鍵相關聯的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" />。

trans-unit.source: Returns a <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> that indicates whether SOAP data transmissions sent to and from this XML Web service are encoded by default.
trans-unit.target: 傳回 <see cref="T:System.Boolean" />，指出往返傳送於這個 XML Web Service 的 SOAP 資料傳輸預設是否已編碼。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if SOAP data transmissions sent to and from this XML Web service are encoded by default; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果往返傳送於這個 XML Web Service 的 SOAP 資料傳輸預設為已編碼，則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.String" /> that contains the namespace to which this XML Web service belongs.
trans-unit.target: 取得 <see cref="T:System.String" />，包含這個 XML Web Service 所屬的命名空間。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that contains the namespace to which this XML Web service belongs.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.String" />，包含這個 XML Web Service 所屬的命名空間。

trans-unit.source: Returns a <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> that indicates whether SOAP messages that are routed to this XML Web service are routed based on the <see langword="SOAPAction" /> HTTP header.
trans-unit.target: 傳回 <see cref="T:System.Boolean" />，指出傳送至這個 XML Web Service 的 SOAP 訊息是否根據 <see langword="SOAPAction" /> HTTP 標頭傳送。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if SOAP messages that are routed to this XML Web service are routed based on the <see langword="SOAPAction" /> HTTP header; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果傳送至這個 XML Web Service 的 SOAP 訊息根據 <see langword="true" /> HTTP 標頭傳送，則為 <see langword="SOAPAction" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。
